    "name": "<p>一天24小时内时针、分针、秒针重合的次数是多少</p>",
    "options": null,
    "answer": "<p>本题可分别分析时针与分针重合的情况以及时针、分针、秒针重合的情况。</p>\n<h3>步骤一：分析时针与分针重合的情况</h3>\n<p>\n  时针每<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>12</mn>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">12</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>小时转一圈，分针每<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>1</mn>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">1</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>小时转一圈，所以分针每转一圈就会与时针重合一次。\n  分针转一圈需要<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>1</mn>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">1</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>小时，时针转一圈需要<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>12</mn>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">12</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>小时，分针的速度是时针速度的<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>12</mn>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">12</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>倍。\n  设时针的角速度为<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mi>ω</mi>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\omega</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>，则分针的角速度为<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>12</mn>\n          <mi>ω</mi>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">12\\omega</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>。从<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>0</mn>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">0</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>点开始，经过<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mi>t</mi>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">t</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>小时后时针与分针重合，此时分针比时针多转了<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mi>n</mi>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>圈（<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mi>n</mi>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>为整数），可列出方程：\n  <span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>12</mn>\n          <mi>ω</mi>\n          <mi>t</mi>\n          <mo>−</mo>\n          <mi>ω</mi>\n          <mi>t</mi>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n          <mi>π</mi>\n          <mi>n</mi>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">12\\omega t - \\omega t = 2\\pi n</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>\n  <span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>11</mn>\n          <mi>ω</mi>\n          <mi>t</mi>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n          <mi>π</mi>\n          <mi>n</mi>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">11\\omega t = 2\\pi n</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>\n  因为时针转一圈<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n          <mi>π</mi>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">2\\pi</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>弧度需要<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>12</mn>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">12</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>小时，即<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mi>ω</mi>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mfrac>\n            <mrow>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n              <mi>π</mi>\n            </mrow>\n            <mn>12</mn>\n          </mfrac>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\omega=\\frac{2\\pi}{12}</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>，代入上式可得：\n  <span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>11</mn>\n          <mo>×</mo>\n          <mfrac>\n            <mrow>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n              <mi>π</mi>\n            </mrow>\n            <mn>12</mn>\n          </mfrac>\n          <mi>t</mi>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n          <mi>π</mi>\n          <mi>n</mi>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">11\\times\\frac{2\\pi}{12}t = 2\\pi n</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>\n  <span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mi>t</mi>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mfrac>\n            <mrow>\n              <mn>12</mn>\n              <mi>n</mi>\n            </mrow>\n            <mn>11</mn>\n          </mfrac>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">t=\\frac{12n}{11}</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>（<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mi>n</mi>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mn>0</mn>\n          <mo separator=\"true\">,</mo>\n          <mn>1</mn>\n          <mo separator=\"true\">,</mo>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n          <mo separator=\"true\">,</mo>\n          <mo>⋯</mo>\n          <mtext> </mtext>\n          <mo separator=\"true\">,</mo>\n          <mn>11</mn>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n = 0,1,2,\\cdots,11</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>）\n  当<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mi>n</mi>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mn>0</mn>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n = 0</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>时，<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mi>t</mi>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mn>0</mn>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">t = 0</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>，即<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>0</mn>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">0</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>点时两针重合；当<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mi>n</mi>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mn>11</mn>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n = 11</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>时，<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mi>t</mi>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mn>12</mn>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">t = 12</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>，即<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>12</mn>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">12</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>点时两针重合。\n  所以在<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>12</mn>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">12</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>小时内，时针与分针重合<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>11</mn>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">11</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>次，那么在<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>24</mn>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">24</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>小时内，时针与分针重合<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>22</mn>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">22</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>次。\n</p>\n<h3>步骤二：分析时针、分针、秒针重合的情况</h3>\n<p>\n  在时针与分针重合的时刻，判断秒针是否也重合。\n  已知时针与分针重合的时刻<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mi>t</mi>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mfrac>\n            <mrow>\n              <mn>12</mn>\n              <mi>n</mi>\n            </mrow>\n            <mn>11</mn>\n          </mfrac>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">t=\\frac{12n}{11}</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>小时，将其换算成秒为<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mi>t</mi>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mfrac>\n            <mrow>\n              <mn>12</mn>\n              <mi>n</mi>\n            </mrow>\n            <mn>11</mn>\n          </mfrac>\n          <mo>×</mo>\n          <mn>3600</mn>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">t=\\frac{12n}{11}\\times3600</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>秒。\n  秒针每<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>60</mn>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">60</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>秒转一圈，即秒针的角速度为<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>60</mn>\n          <mo>×</mo>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n          <mi>π</mi>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">60\\times2\\pi</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>弧度/小时。\n  当<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mi>n</mi>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mn>0</mn>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n = 0</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>时，<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mi>t</mi>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mn>0</mn>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">t = 0</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>，此时时针、分针、秒针都指向<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>12</mn>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">12</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>点，三针重合；当<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mi>n</mi>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mn>11</mn>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n = 11</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>时，<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mi>t</mi>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mn>12</mn>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">t = 12</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>小时，此时时针、分针、秒针又都指向<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>12</mn>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">12</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>点，三针重合。\n  也就是说，在<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>24</mn>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">24</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>小时内，只有<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>0</mn>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">0</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>点和<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>12</mn>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">12</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>点这两个时刻时针、分针、秒针是重合的，所以重合次数是<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">2</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>次。\n</p>\n<p>综上，一天<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>24</mn>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">24</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>小时内时针、分针、秒针重合的次数是<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <semantics>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n        </mrow>\n        <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">2</annotation>\n      </semantics>\n    </math></span>次。</p>",
